You just transformed the puzzle from &quot;annoying&quot; to &quot;can teach a worthwhile lesson&quot; for me.<p>Edit: This message can be made more clear with a slight change to the puzzle.<p>There are two methods, foo and bar. One returns what you desire.<p><pre><code>    /** Exactly one of the comments is true */
